{
  "stem": "5516.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So before holiday, he used to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He used to bless them-- Mhm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know [LAUGHS] And he used to bring the blessing to the family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of the war?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The war started in Poland and Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we was on the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think this got nothing to do with Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the Russian took over Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's the same like [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sometime a storm comes in here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they know a couple-odd hours before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened-- how they took over Lithuania is the Russian, Stalin's government, called in the Secretary of State of Lithuania when he was in Moscow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the same time when he was there, the tanks from Russia crossed the border.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's next to it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they occupied Lithuania, Latvia, and Estonia in a few hours, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know they will come in--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--see.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we didn't know this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe we had an idea because, you see, when the war started, Poland and Germany-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so after the First World War, they proclaimed Lithuania a country.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the capital was Vilna for hundreds or thousands of years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after the war, when they proclaimed Poland and all the countries independent-- and Lithuania, it's a general from Poland, without saying to nobody, he just-- in with his army when he's occupied Vilna, the capital.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Lithuania didn't have a capital for a long time, for 25 years, maybe, 28 years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't have diplomatic relation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't send even a letter, even it's next door because they was in a rift, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After this, Poland gave ultimatum to Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After 28 years, if you don't make diplomatic relation with us, we will occupy.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
